Class MutationLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • mutation.MutationLibrary

  • public class MutationLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class MutationDictonary. the class is using a java Hashtable only allowing to add multiple items in one key. (By chaining method using LinkedList)
